ygData.messageBody:
I'm still around but took the last 2 weeks off for back to school and
various other stuff. My plan was to get everything around the house caught
up and maybe a bit ahead before PoP, but now it looks like I will need to
get back on the raid horse. I really don't care for raid level stuff, all
hurry up and wait. Plus I finally got a new job and have to log at a
reasonable hour. Being on EST, that means I have to go about the time we get
really started in VT or wherever. Songs are the only thing I care about
having though so it's back to grind, I suppose.

Brilinnia Ban'Sidhe 60 Bard
Brilinia Ilsidi 54 wizard
Brillinia Klagetsdautter 46 cleric
Venator Sapentia, Xegony
